Discovered a whole new side of Ibiza from our stay at @7PinesIbiza. From the magic of Es Vedrà & unimaginable sunsets in the west, to the iconic old town in the south & the awe-striking and serene coast in the north, the destination has something for everyone.

📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

node.text:
Enjoying the peace and quiet with @tattivasilieva. 🛌 Located in Kaluga, Neotipi in Pine River is a destination meant to inspire you to recharge your spirits and reconnect with yourself. 🍃 

Neotipi gives you unhindered views of the surrounding nature, making your stay a truly memorable one without the usual noise and distractions. You'll be immersed in the therapeutic melodies of nature with starry nights and morning skies above your head. If you need to detach from the usual, Neotipi is where you need to be! ⛺

Are you in dire need of a vacation? Do you also like nature stays?

📸 @tattivasilieva
📍 @neotipi, Kaluga, Russia

node.text:
Be inspired like @traveljeanieous with this gorgeous view of Gaudi's La Sagrada Familia. ⛪ The Ayre Hotel Rosellón in Barcelona has surreal panoramic rooftop views of the city and is barely 200 meters away from the most iconic basilica in Spain. 🇪🇸

💡BH Trivia: Did you know that La Sagrada Familia has been under construction for over a century? This year it has been believed to have entered its final stage of construction and is estimated to be completed by 2026. 

When was the last time you visited Barcelona? What was your first reaction upon seeing this treasure? ❤

📽️ @traveljeanieous
📍 @ayrehoteles, Barcelona, Spain
🎶 Andrea Bocelli - Bésame Mucho

Have you visited Puri Santrian? When was the last time you visited Bali?

There's plenty of opportunities to encounter wildlife from a distance, immerse in local culture, and reconnect with one's self by deeply immersing in the tropics. ❤

Have you been to Holbox Island? Are you a fan of eco-hotels? 🌿

📽 @pierreschuester

Catching rainbows with @reneeroaming. 🌈 At Intercontinental French Polynesia, holidays can't be ruined by a little drizzle. 🌦️

Want to maximize this dream getaway? Step off the deck of your overwater villa into the warm embrace of their tranquil lagoon. Enjoy everything from scuba diving to sunset cruises to explore their majestic reefs and discover the thriving underwater wildlife. It's a once-in-a-lifetime experience so you better book that next flight to Bora Bora!

Tell us about your favorite tropical getaway stay. 💭 

📽️ @reneeroaming
📍 @icfr_polynesia
🎶 Israel Kamakawiwo'ole - Somewhere Over The Rainbow/What A Wonderful World

Afternoon stroll by the pool with @david_maman. 🇮🇩 Perched on the edge of the Petanu River canyon, Alami Villa gives you the ultimate escape as you are soothed by the flowing river, the ever-present breeze, and the verdant surroundings. 🍃 

In Balinese, "alami" means being one with nature. Reconnect with Mother Nature as you take in the views, the forest melody, and the jungle vibe from your villa. 😌

Do you love these types of views? Are you looking forward to visiting Bali soon? 

📸 @david_maman
📍 @alamivilla, Indonesia

Basking in the glory of the rain with @antonio.pozo at Dusit Thani Maldives. 🌧️ Mood can't be dampened by any weather when you're staying at an overwater villa, don't you think?

At Dusit Thani Maldives, you'll have something to do rain or shine! Let the sounds of the rain melt away your stress while doing a yoga session with their resident yogi, or go on an excursion to swim with sharks and manta rays in the sea. 🌊

How was your last visit to the Maldives? Are you looking at flying there again? 🇲🇻

📽️ @antonio.pozo
📍 @dusit.hotels, Baa Atoll, Maldives
🎶 Danheim - Kala
